vote.title: Authorize acquisition of six parcels of land containing a total of approximately 144,940 square feet located near the intersection of West Redbird Lane and Pastor Bailey Drive for the Dallas Executive Airport (list attached to the Agenda Information Sheet) - Not to exceed $244,000.00 ($226,000.00, plus closing costs and title expenses not to exceed $18,000.00) - Financing: Aviation Fund
